<br />Because none of the current emulators map tile numbers to pieces of polygon mesh. If they did, SMB1 could be made to look like <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q9k3XBQ59yk" class="postlink">it does in Brawl</a>. That would be an interesting research project: imagine the "high resolution texture packs" for N64 games taken up to 11.

		

